READ ME

Validations
1. Name - include validation of using special characters ()
        - ensure Case sensitive validation
2. Date - still visible in e-form but is autogenerated in current date and cannot be edited by the user
3. Age - Age should be within the range between 18 and 99.
4. Captcha - before Submit button
5. Feedback Message - a message will appear once the e-form is submitted
                    - new page/modal
6. Refresh Button/Redirect Button - put under the feedback message. For redirecting another response for the other user.


// Age script according to phind

<form id="ageForm">
    Age: <input type="number" id="age" name="age" min="18" max="99" required>
    <input type="submit" value="Submit">
</form>

<script>
document.getElementById('ageForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {
    var age = document.getElementById('age').value;
    if (age < 18 || age > 99) {
        alert('Age must be between 18 and 99.');
        event.preventDefault(); // Prevent form submission
    }
});
</script>
